    "This is in line with studies suggesting founders should avoid emphasising risk or relying too much on emotional appeal over credibility (Majumdar and Bose, 2018).",
    "Psychological ownership is viewed positively in crowdfunding (Nesij Huvaj et al., 2023).",
    "Yet in this case there may be a fine line between making potential funders feel they are part of the campaign or leaving them suspicious of whether it can succeed without them.",
